* Trained and qualified emergency response teams composed of MeadWestvaco employees are on-site around the clock take prompt action using the facility's fire truck, ambulance, and hazardous materials unit;
* Emergency response systems in place, including plant wide alarms, radios linked to North Charleston Fire Department, and an accessible water supply;
